text: Luna Rami Amin Al-Masri (; born 9 March 1994) is a Jordanian footballer who plays as an attacking midfielder for Lebanese club Safa. ==Club career== Al- Masri joined Safa in 2020; she scored one goal and made one assist in four games in the 2019–20 season. ==References== == External links == * Category:Living people Category:1994 births Category:Sportspeople from Amman Category:Jordanian women's footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Jordan women's international footballers Category:Lebanese Women's Football League players Category:Jordanian expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Lebanon Category:Jordanian expatriate sportspeople in Lebanon Category:Safa WFC players
